typeIdent.description:
Indicates explicit sub-type of entry.  Composed of the concatenation of the typeKey of the instance's type and all
of its base type's typeIdent

id.description:
A unique identifier that can be manually assigned or generated automatically during object creation. This
identifier cannot be altered after the object has been persisted.

version.description:
Version number used for optimistic concurrency.  Automatically managed by the system.

Updating an Obj with a null or 0 value for version will cause the concurrency check to be skipped and should only
be done with great caution.

typeWithBindings.description: Persists concrete type with bindings for generic types where instance has parameter bindings

bulbType.description: The bulb type for this bulb.

manufacturer.description: The name of this bulb's manufacturer.

startDate.description: The time at which this bulb was manufactured.

bulbMeasurements.description: The measurements associated with this smart bulb.

currentFixture.description: The current fixture this bulb is installed in.

fixtureHistory.description: The history of fixtures this bulb has been installed in.

bulbStatus.description:
The current status of the bulb based on the latest measurement.
0 = Off, 1 = On, 2 = Burned Out
This is a stored calculated property that retrieves the latest status from measurements.

lifeSpanInHours.description: The lifespan of the CFL bulb in hours.

efficiencyFactor.description: The energy efficiency factor of the CFL bulb.
